    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Dec 22, 2016</title>
      <link>//cloudfeed.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2016-12-22/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Dec 2016 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//cloudfeed.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2016-12-22/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Cool as McCumber: Data Breach Fatigue&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every vendor and consultancy firm ensured breach detection and response services were touted at the top of their list of offerings. The entire &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.securityinfowatch.com/article/12283388/data-breach-fatigue&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.securityinfowatch.com/article/12283388/data-breach-fatigue&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Supercharge Your SIEM with Threat Hunting&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Security Information Event Management (SIEM) tools with threat hunting.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.dlt.com/blog/2016/12/21/supercharge-siem-threat-hunting/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.dlt.com/blog/2016/12/21/supercharge-siem-threat-hunting/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;State delegate blasts response to FCPS data breach, promises legislation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data breaches and student privacy are a large concern, said Marc Rotenberg, the president and executive director of the Electronic Privacy &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.fredericknewspost.com/news/education/state-delegate-blasts-response-to-fcps-data-breach-promises-legislation/article_e2095e79-9db0-5dd5-80c6-755fe926751f.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.fredericknewspost.com/news/education/state-delegate-blasts-response-to-fcps-data-breach-promises-legislation/article_e2095e79-9db0-5dd5-80c6-755fe926751f.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Akamai buys a vendor that targets malicious bots&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; a vendor that aims to help companies stop bots and malicious automated traffic that use stolen credentials, such as emails and passwords, to log in &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.b2becommerceworld.com/2016/12/21/akamai-buys-vendor-targets-malicious-bots&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.b2becommerceworld.com/2016/12/21/akamai-buys-vendor-targets-malicious-bots&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;All about data security: Policy, processes and flow&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; many boards have become more aware of the risks of data breaches to the company&amp;rsquo;s reputation and brand, and the dangers of the loss of customer &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.enterpriseinnovation.net/article/all-about-data-security-policy-processes-and-flow-843498771&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.enterpriseinnovation.net/article/all-about-data-security-policy-processes-and-flow-843498771&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Cyberwar investigates North Korea, Russia hacking&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; world had learned a big lesson through things such as the Sony hack and filming this documentary showed him just how real data breaches can be.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.news.com.au/technology/online/hacking/cyberwar-investigates-north-korea-russia-hacking/news-story/205f21c197895e4ff95a28d53e6bc691&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.news.com.au/technology/online/hacking/cyberwar-investigates-north-korea-russia-hacking/news-story/205f21c197895e4ff95a28d53e6bc691&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Government commits to EU GDPR data rules post 2018&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;hefty fines for data breaches will be introduced  up to 20 million or 4% of global annual turnover for the preceding financial year, whichever is the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://diginomica.com/2016/12/22/government-commits-eu-gdpr-data-rules-post-2018/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://diginomica.com/2016/12/22/government-commits-eu-gdpr-data-rules-post-2018/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data breach fines to jump following EU GDPR adoption&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; in the UK, the government has confirmed, increasing ICO&amp;rsquo;s maximum monetary penalty for data breaches from 500,000 to 20 million or more.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.bit-tech.net/news/bits/2016/12/22/data-breach-fines-to-jump/1?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+bit-tech%2Fall+%28bit-tech.net+feed%29&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.bit-tech.net/news/bits/2016/12/22/data-breach-fines-to-jump/1?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+bit-tech%2Fall+%28bit-tech.net+feed%29&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;TrapX Reveals 2016 Healthcare Breaches Increased 63 Percent Year-Over-Year;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yahoo Sports The data also shows sophisticated cyber attackers are now responsible for 31.42 percent of all major HIPAA data breaches reported in 2016, which is &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://sports.yahoo.com/news/trapx-reveals-2016-healthcare-breaches-110000095.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://sports.yahoo.com/news/trapx-reveals-2016-healthcare-breaches-110000095.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;What can we expect from cyber-security in 2017?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Over two billion personal records were stolen this year alone in a series of data breaches that included Yahoo, MySpace and the National Lottery.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.itproportal.com/features/what-can-we-expect-from-cyber-security-in-2017/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.itproportal.com/features/what-can-we-expect-from-cyber-security-in-2017/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

